THE ONE WITH MY GIRLS🩶🤍🖤

We have know each other for more than 10 years now and like @anjali_ajith_2903 wrote 🙈 it feels like we are just getting started . These are the kind of friendships that last forever no matter what city you live in or how often you speak, no matter how old you get or what phase of life you are in. It’s the type friendship that has no judgement and sticks by you even when you f*ck up. 
Its not always the ones around you , but those with you , who will really show you through when you are at your lowest . That’s when you see the gems admist the stones.

Here’s to the friends. The ones who make your world a little less chaotic . 
The ones who know just what to say at just the right times. 
The ones who make you laugh so hard you cry. The ones who are there for the mess, the magic, the mundane and all the moments in between. 
The ones who are ready to stand up for you, fight for you, and protect you at all costs. 
The ones who are there- no matter what.Ily 🫂❤️

Ps: this is the first time documenting our time together in yearsss lol , ik 🙈 it was fun tho😂
